{"title_hebrew":"והיא שעמדה","title_english":"Vehi Sheamda","artist":"Traditional / Yonatan Razel","overview":"A central text from the Passover Haggadah. It reminds us that in every generation, enemies rise against the Jewish people, but God saves them from their hands. Razel's melody made it a modern classic.","youtube_url":"https://youtu.be/DjPqwkd4-uc?si=t8-VhPzHm9G0EH6U","lyrics":[{"hebrew":"והיא שעמדה, והיא שעמדה","transliteration":"Vehi she'amda, vehi she'amda","english":"And it is this [promise] that has stood"},{"hebrew":"לאבותינו ולנו","transliteration":"La'avoteinu velanu","english":"For our fathers and for us"},{"hebrew":"והיא שעמדה, והיא שעמדה","transliteration":"Vehi she'amda, vehi she'amda","english":"And it is this [promise] that has stood"},{"hebrew":"לאבותינו ולנו","transliteration":"La'avoteinu velanu","english":"For our fathers and for us"},{"hebrew":"שלא אחד בלבד","transliteration":"Shelo echad bilvad","english":"For not just one alone"},{"hebrew":"עמד עלינו לכלותינו","transliteration":"Amad aleinu lechaloteinu","english":"Has stood against us to destroy us"},{"hebrew":"שלא אחד בלבד","transliteration":"Shelo echad bilvad","english":"For not just one alone"},{"hebrew":"עמד עלינו לכלותינו","transliteration":"Amad aleinu lechaloteinu","english":"Has stood against us to destroy us"},{"hebrew":"אלא שבכל דור ודור","transliteration":"Ela shebechol dor vador","english":"But in every generation"},{"hebrew":"עומדים עלינו לכלותינו","transliteration":"Omdim aleinu lechaloteinu","english":"They stand against us to destroy us"},{"hebrew":"אלא שבכל דור ודור","transliteration":"Ela shebechol dor vador","english":"But in every generation"},{"hebrew":"עומדים עלינו לכלותינו","transliteration":"Omdim aleinu lechaloteinu","english":"They stand against us to destroy us"},{"hebrew":"והקדוש ברוך הוא מצילנו מידם","transliteration":"VehaKadosh Baruch Hu matzilenu miyadam","english":"And the Holy One, Blessed be He, saves us from their hand"},{"hebrew":"והקדוש ברוך הוא מצילנו מידם","transliteration":"VehaKadosh Baruch Hu matzilenu miyadam","english":"And the Holy One, Blessed be He, saves us from their hand"}]}